@companyApiBase = http://localhost:8081
@baseUrl = {{companyApiBase}}

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List companies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/companies

### Get company by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/companies/1

### Create company
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/companies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "NewCo Inc",
  "industry": "Services"
}

### Swagger/OpenAPI
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json
